vulnerability.name: USN-5739-2
vulnerability.description: USN-5739-1 fixed vulnerabilities in MariaDB. It caused a regression. This update fixes the problem.  We apologize for the inconvenience.  Original advisory details:   MariaDB has been updated to 10.3.38 in Ubuntu 20.04 LTS and to 10.6.12  in Ubuntu 22.04 LTS and Ubuntu 22.10.
